illegally dropping cigarette butts.

01:15:06.666 --> 01:15:09.332
l would like to recommend
the fine be increased

01:15:09.333 --> 01:15:14.540
to a minimum of $1 million
as a stronger deterrent

01:15:14.583 --> 01:15:17.957
and would be happy...

01:15:32.958 --> 01:15:36.457
(Max groans)

01:15:45.708 --> 01:15:47.832
(Warning bell rings)

01:15:51.083 --> 01:15:54.832
Thank you.

