01:22:25.000 --> 01:22:28.957
When l received your book,
the emotions inside my brain

01:22:28.958 --> 01:22:34.040
felt like they were in a tumble dryer,
smashing into each other.

01:22:35.250 --> 01:22:39.707
The hurt felt like when l accidentally
stapled my lips together.

01:22:39.708 --> 01:22:41.415
Ow!

01:22:41.500 --> 01:22:46.999
The reason l forgive you
is because you are not perfect.

01:22:47.000 --> 01:22:50.999
You are imperfect, and so am l.

01:22:51.000 --> 01:22:53.999
All humans are imperfect,

01:22:54.000 --> 01:22:58.415
even the man outside my apartment
who litters.

01:22:58.458 --> 01:23:04.915
When l was young,
l wanted to be anybody but myself.

01:23:04.958 --> 01:23:08.957
Dr Bernard Hazelhof said
if l was on a desert island

01:23:08.958 --> 01:23:12.665
then l would have to get used
to my own company -

01:23:12.666 --> 01:23:15.915
just me and the coconuts.

01:23:15.958 --> 01:23:22.540
He said l would have to accept myself,
my warts and all,

01:23:22.583 --> 01:23:25.540
and that we don't get to choose
our warts.

01:23:25.541 --> 01:23:29.207
They are a part of us
and we have to live with them.

01:23:31.041 --> 01:23:35.207
We can, however, choose our friends

01:23:35.208 --> 01:23:40.540
and l am glad l have chosen you.

01:23:40.541 --> 01:23:43.707
Dr Bernard Hazelhof also said

01:23:43.750 --> 01:23:48.249
that everyone's lives
are like a very long sidewalk.

01:23:48.250 --> 01:23:52.957
Some are well paved.
Others, like mine,

01:23:52.958 --> 01:23:58.540
have cracks, banana skins
and cigarette butts.

01:23:58.541 --> 01:24:05.540
Your sidewalk is like mine
but probably not as many cracks.

01:24:05.583 --> 01:24:09.582
Hopefully, one day
our sidewalks will meet

01:24:09.666 --> 01:24:13.249
and we can share
a can of condensed milk.

01:24:14.875 --> 01:24:17.040
(She slurps)

01:24:17.041 --> 01:24:23.332
You are my best friend.
You are my only friend.

01:24:23.375 --> 01:24:28.790
Your American penpal,
Max Jerry Horowitz.

01:24:30.041 --> 01:24:35.040
PS. l have recently found the perfect job
with a survey company.

01:24:35.041 --> 01:24:39.874
All l have to do is eat things
and tick boxes.

